trans-unit.source: Defines the abstract base class for composable parts, which import objects and produce exported objects.
trans-unit.target: Define la clase base abstracta para los elementos susceptibles de composición, que importan objetos y producen objetos exportados.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: Called when all the imports of the part have been set, and exports can be retrieved.
trans-unit.target: Se invoca cuando se han establecido todas las importaciones del elemento y se pueden recuperar las exportaciones.

trans-unit.source: Once this method is called, no further imports can be set unless a call is made to Deactivate.
trans-unit.target: Una vez que se llama a este método, no se puede establecer ninguna importación más, a menos que se realiza una llamada a desactivar.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the exported objects provided by the part.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> que describen los objetos exportados proporcionados por el elemento.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the exported objects provided by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: Colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> que describen los objetos exportados proporcionados por <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ExportDefinitions%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto creado desde un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propiedad debe devolver el resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ExportDefinitions%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Las invalidaciones de esta propiedad nunca deberían devolver `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not have exports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> no tiene exportaciones, devolver vacío <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> colección en su lugar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> se ha eliminado.

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects from the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> property that describes the exported object to return.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> de la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> que describe el objeto exportado que se va a devolver.

trans-unit.source: Gets the exported object described by the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto exportado descrito por el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The exported object described by <paramref name="definition" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto exportado descrito por <paramref name="definition" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> se ha eliminado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="definition" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="definition" /> es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred getting the exported object described by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Se produjo un error al obtener el objeto exportado descrito por <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="definition" /> did not originate from the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> property on the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="definition" /> no se originó en la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: One or more prerequisite imports, indicated by <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition.IsPrerequisite" />, have not been set.
trans-unit.target: No se han establecido una o varias de las importaciones que constituyen un requisito previo y que vienen indicadas por <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition.IsPrerequisite" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imported objects required by the part.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> que describen los objetos importados que necesita el elemento.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imported objects required by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: Colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> que describen los objetos importados que necesita el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ImportDefinitions%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto creado desde un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propiedad debe devolver el resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ImportDefinitions%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Las invalidaciones de esta propiedad nunca deberían devolver `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> no tiene importaciones, devolver vacío <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> colección en su lugar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> se ha eliminado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene los metadatos del objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: The metadata of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Metadatos del objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> object.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es un objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> vacío de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.Metadata%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto creado desde un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propiedad debe devolver el resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.Metadata%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Las invalidaciones de esta propiedad deben devolver solo lectura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objeto con un comparador entre mayúsculas y minúsculas, no lingüística, como <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>y nunca debe devolver `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> instead.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> no contienen metadatos, devolver vacío <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> en su lugar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> se ha eliminado.

trans-unit.source: One of the objects from the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ImportDefinitions" /> property that specifies the import to be set.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los objetos de la propiedad <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ImportDefinitions" /> que especifica la importación que se va a establecer.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export" /> objects of which to set the import described by <c>definition</c>.
trans-unit.target: Colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export" /> para los que se va a establecer la importación descrita por <c>definition</c>.

trans-unit.source: Sets the import described by the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> object to be satisfied by the specified exports.
trans-unit.target: Establece la importación descrita por el objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> especificado que deben satisfacer las exportaciones especificadas.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: El objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> se ha eliminado.
